Megabonus Cash Back Service is an easy way to make more profitable purchases in 2,000+ popular stores and services all over the world. 


Install the extension and do everything as usual. We will take care of making your purchases economical and safe. 

•	Cash Back up to 40% in more than 2,000 popular stores an services from all over the world including the universal appeal AliExpress;
•      Price tracker;
•	Flexible Megabonus Loyalty Program consisting of 7 levels. The more you buy, the higher your level and cash back rate is;
•	Cash back notifications and convenient activation. You won’t forget to activate cash back before purchasing and get your cash back;
•	AliExpress seller check. Make not only profitable but also safe purchases on Ali;
•	Display of your cash back sum. Learn your cach back sum before paying  for the product. This is really convenient!
•	Notices on cash back crediting  - as soon as we get the information on your cash back, we will immediately inform you;
•	Quick withdrawal in a convenient way. Cash back can be withdrawn to: a bank card, PayPal, Webmoney, Yandex.Money and to a mobile;
•	Package Search. The possibility to track the location of your parcel using the tracking number right in the extension;
•	Friendly and professional support service.



With this extension, you won’t need other ones for the work with AliExpress. We took the best solutions for AliExpress and united everything in one product to make your purchases on AliExpress economical and safe. 


We will be glad to see you among the millions of Megabonus.com users from all over the world making smart purchases with Megabonus even now.

With love, your Megabonus Cash Back Service!

Installing Megabonus extension you accept the provisions of the User Agreement and allow redirecting you by the extension through the links of the partner programs Megabonus Cash Back Service is connected to. 


This is also to inform you that the extension uses Google Analytics service to collect the usage statistics to improve your user experience. In case you don’t want to send your data to Google Analytics, please go to: http://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout or add filtering in Adblock Plus or with the help of other ad-blocking apps.



Megabonus extension uses the following rights due to the below-mentioned reasons:

(a)	tabs –– the user acquires the opportunity to activate cash back from the corresponding element of the extension’s interface; the user gets opportunities to get notifications on cash back automatic activation in the corresponding element of the extension’s interface if this type of automatization is available when on the current webpage of the product.
(b)	activeTabs – the system of color notifications allowing to identify the extensions’ work status when on the current webpage of the product becomes available to the user in the corresponding element of the extension’s interface; grey color of the extension’s icon – cash back is not available on this webpage; yellow color of the extension’s icon – cash back is available on this webpage and its status is being defined; red color of the extension’s icon – cash back is available on this page but it is currently blocked for the user by a third-party service; green color of the extension’s icon – cash back is available on this page and it’s properly activated for the user.


(c)	webRequest – the extension analyzes the absence of blocking factors for the proper activation of cash back for the user and informs them through a corresponding element of the extension’s interface. 
(d)	webRequestBlocking – a reliable way of cash back activation is available to the user when on the products’ webpages  of online stores; if third-party services are trying to block it, the user is informed on it through a corresponding element of the extensions’ interface. 
(e)	cookies – detecting cash back blocking by third-party services and giving notice of the circumstance to the user in the corresponding element of the extension’s interface; the user gets an opportunity of being informed about the online stores meeting their interests in the corresponding element of the extension’s interface. 
(f)	notifications – sending the user push-up messages in the browser with the information on cash back status (credited, confirmed, declined), on new opportunities and actions and other system messages in accordance with the User Agreement;
(g)	http(s)://*/* – using the extension the user has access to all its functionality in regards to the actual database of all online stores the cash back is available to the user in – there’s no need for the user to wait for the extension’s update to get cash back in the stores that have recently joined the service.

